&lt;p&gt;解决 &lt;code&gt;OpenSSL SSL_read: Connection was reset, errno 10054&lt;/code&gt; &lt;br&gt;
 &lt;code&gt;git config --global http.sslVerify &amp;quot;false&amp;quot;&lt;/code&gt; &lt;br&gt;
 解决 &lt;code&gt;Failed to connect to github.com port 443: Timed out&lt;/code&gt; &lt;br&gt;
 &lt;code&gt;git config --global https.proxy &lt;/code&gt; &lt;br&gt;
 &lt;code&gt;git config --global --unset https.proxy&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
